OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A New York school has apologised after 
OL,6, serving what it called an "inexcusably 
OL,7, insensitive" lunch on the first day of 
OL,8, Black History Month.                   
OL,10,FStudents at Nyack Middle School were   
OL,11,Fserved fried chicken, waffles and      
OL,12,Fwatermelon on 1 February.              
OL,14,FThe foods have been used as racist     
OL,15,Ftropes against African Americans.      
OL,17,FOfficials from the school said its food
OL,18,Fsupplier - Aramark - had changed the   
OL,19,Fplanned meal of cheesesteaks, broccoli 
OL,20,Fand fruit.                             
